<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030494-0101 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 019371 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 4, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
