and Mike Christensen said in a report. 
</P>
<P>
 Gray and Plourde were uninjured, the report said. 
</P>
<P>
 Velador was taken to Westlake Hospital with multiple injuries and admitted in 
critical condition. He died less than two hours later, deputies reported. 
</P>
<P>
 There was no indication any of the drivers was intoxicated at the time, and 
deputies said they are still investigating the crash. MACK REED 
