<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 142-98-1 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Josh 
Hochgesang Jr. SS R-R Scott Monson Jr. 2B R-R Keith Wescott Sr. 3B R-R 
