<P>
 * Television: Germany's Bertelsmann is linking with France's Canal Plus in a 
joint venture to develop internationally "non-advertising-financed" television 
such as pay TV, pay-per-view and video-on-demand services. Bertelsmann Chief 
Executive Mark Woessner and Canal Plus Chief Executive Pierre Lescure signed 
