<TEXT>
<P>
 Life insurance -- A story Tuesday incorrectly ranked Pacific Mutual Life 
Insurance Co. in Newport Beach. It is the state's largest insurer based on 
assets, but Transamerica Occidental Life had $275 billion of life insurance in 
force at the end of 1992. 
</P>
