<P>
 Art project -- The Earthquake Memorial Project, an outdoor tile mosaic being 
created by L.A. artists out of items broken during the disaster, will be 
installed near the vicinity of the collapse of the Interstate 10 freeway, not 
at the L.A. Children's Museum as stated in Tuesday's Calendar. 
</P>
